on</span><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="16" width="16" class="e3009e"><path d="M8.75 7.25V0h-1.5v7.25H0v1.5h7.25V16h1.5V8.75H16v-1.5H8.75Z"></path></svg></button><div id="section-descriptionAccordion" aria-labelledby="toggle-descriptionAccordion" aria-hidden="true" hidden="" class="f88a58 e57e56" role="region"><div class=""><div class="aa8f50 e1833d"><div class="b0b19c"><span class="b04b30 d63583">H&amp;M Premium Selection</span></div><p class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 b493f8">Elasticized scrunchies in mulberry silk for reduced damage to hair.</p><p class="b04b30 f55cde" data-testid="description-article-number">Art. No.:<!-- --> <!-- -->1107467007</p><dl class="a4c5da"><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Pieces/Pairs: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-pieces">4</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Description: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-detailedDescriptions">Black, Solid colour</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Accessory Style: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-accessoriesStyle">Scrunchie</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Nice to know: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-niceToKnow">H&amp;M Premium Selection</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Quantity: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-quantitySalesMode">N/A</dd></div></dl></div></div></div></div><div class="dafb45"><button type="button" class="a2e9ad b34f1f edb270" aria-expanded="false" aria-disabled="false" id="toggle-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion" aria-controls="section-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion"><span class="f96cb6">Materials</span><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="16" width="16" class="e3009e"><path d="M8.75 7.25V0h-1.5v7.25H0v1.5h7.25V16h1.5V8.75H16v-1.5H8.75Z"></path></svg></button><div id="section-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion" aria-labelledby="toggle-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion" aria-hidden="true" hidden="" class="f88a58 e57e56" role="region"><div class=""><div class="aa8f50 e1833d"><div class="b103ee"><h3 class="b9e19c b1dbab c3f7b3">Composition</h3><ul class="b2b6a8"><li class="b819ff"><span class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 d20aac">Silk 100%</span></li></ul></div><dl class="b103ee"><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Material: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7">Silk</dd></div></dl><section class="b103ee"><h3 class="b9e19c b1dbab c3f7b3">Materials in this product explained</h3><dl><div><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd f32842">Silk</dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 d9737e">Silk is a delicate, natural protein fibre obtained from the cocoons of silkworms.</dd></div></dl></section></div></div></div></div><div class="dafb45"><button type="button" class="a2e9ad b34f1f edb270" aria-expanded="false" aria-disabled="false" id="toggle-careGuideAccordion" aria-controls="section-careGuideAccordion"><span class="f96cb6">Care guide</span><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="16" width="16" class="e3009e"><path d="M8.75 7.25V0h-1.5v7.25H0v1.5h7.25V16h1.5V8.75H16v-1.5H8.75Z"></path></svg></button><div id="section-careGuideAccordion" aria-labelledby="toggle-careGuideAccordion" aria-hidden="true" hidden="" class="f88a58 e57e56" role="region"><div class=""><div class="aa8f50 e1833d"><p class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 c35328">Bring your clean, previously loved clothing or textiles to one of our stores — they can be from any brand.</p><a class="d810bb def1f3" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/sustainability-at-hm/take-care/take-care.html">Read about how you can make your clothes last longer</a><section><h3 class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd ce9134">Care instructions</h3><ul class="e00dc3"><li class="cf312e e8d6d7">Medium iron</li><li class="cf312e e8d6d7">Machine wash at 40° Gentle cycle​</li><li class="cf312e e8d6d7">No dry clean</li><li class="cf312e e8d6d7">Line dry</li><li class="cf312e e8d6d7">Only non-chlorine bleach when needed</li></ul></section></div></div></div></div><div class="dafb45"><button type="button" class="a2e9ad b34f1f edb270" aria-expanded="false" aria-disabled="false" id="toggle-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion" aria-controls="section-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion"><span class="f96cb6">Delivery and Payment</span><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="16" width="16" class="e3009e"><path d="M8.75 7.25V0h-1.5v7.25H0v1.5h7.25V16h1.5V8.75H16v-1.5H8.75Z"></path></svg></button><div id="section-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion" aria-labelledby="toggle-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion" aria-hidden="true" hidden="" class="f88a58 e57e56" role="region"><div class=""><div class="aa8f50 e1833d"><div><p class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 ca6d2d">Delivery in 6-12 business days</p><p class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 ca6d2d">Free delivery on all orders over PHP 2,499. For orders below, PHP 2,499, a shipping fee of PHP 149 will be applied. ​ Your parcel will be delivered to your home or an alternate address within the following business days: NCR: 6-8 days, Luzon: 8-10 days, Visayas:9-10 days, Mindanao: 10-12 days. At the moment, all orders are shipping out from our warehouse in Malaysia. Occasionally, you may experience a longer delivery lead time, especially during sales periods. PAYMENT: We accept MasterCard, Visa credit cards and cash on delivery. Learn more on our customer service pages.​</p><p class="beae19 ca6d2d" data-testid="customer-service-information">For more information, please visit our Customer Service pages for <a class="d810bb def1f3" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/customer-service/delivery.html" aria-label="Delivery information">Delivery</a>, <a class="d810bb def1f3" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/customer-service/payments-info.html" aria-label="Payment information">Payments</a> and <a class="d810bb def1f3" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/customer-service/returns.html" aria-label="Return information">Returns</a>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="e0bbeb f83365 f0e4eb"></div><div class="__9HO5"></div><nav class="fabd1f vSBc" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><ol class="b43307 ea1998"><li class="be557b"><a class="e70853 ca9a38" href="/en_ph/index.html">HM.com</a><span class="fdb3e1 bf7a7c e33bd7" role="presentation">/</span></li><li class="be557b"><a class="e70853 ca9a38" href="/en_ph/ladies.html">Women</a><span class="fdb3e1 bf7a7c e33bd7" role="presentation">/</span></li><li class="be557b"><a class="e70853 ca9a38" href="/en_ph/ladies/shop-by-product/premium-selection.html">Premium Selection</a><span class="fdb3e1 bf7a7c e33bd7" role="presentation">/</span></li><li class="be557b"><a class="e70853 ca9a38" href="/en_ph/ladies/shop-by-product/premium-selection/accessories.html">Accessories</a><span class="fdb3e1 bf7a7c e33bd7" role="presentation">/</span></li><li class="be557b de188b"><a class="e70853 ca9a38 b7d289" data-testid="selected-breadcrumb" href="/en_ph/productpage.1107467007.html" aria-current="page">4-pack Silk Scrunchies</a></li></ol></nav></main><footer class="ce4712"><div class="ca43aa"><nav aria-labelledby="Shop"><h2 class="b9e19c ff123f a0c8b9" id="Shop">Shop</h2><ul class="de51f5"><li class="c3919b"><a class="e70853" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/ladies.html">Women</a></li><li class="c3919b"><a class="e70853" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/men.html">Men</a></li><li class="c3919b"><a class="e70853" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/kids.html">Kids</a></li></ul></nav><nav aria-labelledby="Corporate_Info"><h2 class="b9e19c ff123f a0c8b9" id="Corporate_Info">Corporate Info</h2><ul class="de51f5"><li class="c3919b"><a class="e70853" href="https://career.hm.com/">Career at H&amp;M</a></li><li class="c3919b"><a class="e708